01:13:18,110 --> 01:13:18,943
Freeze!

815
01:13:19,736 --> 01:13:20,376
Damn it!

816
01:13:20,623 --> 01:13:21,590
He's fake.

817
01:13:23,160 --> 01:13:24,913
Drop the pistol.

818
01:13:25,197 --> 01:13:25,743
Stay away.

819
01:13:26,877 --> 01:13:28,143
I'll kill him.

820
01:13:33,808 --> 01:13:35,775
We knew you'd come.

821
01:13:37,213 --> 01:13:39,567
