823
01:13:44,878 --> 01:13:46,178
Long time no see,Kyohei.

824
01:13:47,140 --> 01:13:48,673
You grew up.

825
01:13:49,801 --> 01:13:52,508
You grew up on bad things.

826
01:13:54,886 --> 01:13:58,619
You seem to know too much about us that we don't want you to know.

827
01:13:58,892 --> 01:14:01,526
I know about Ube and Koyama.

828
01:14:04,851 --> 01:14:08,038
I sent my notes and the tape recording to the police before I came here.

829
01:14:09,210 --> 01:14:10,270
Don't worry about it.

830
01:14:11,198 --> 01:14:14,151
As long as this man is not alive, none of that stuff will works.

831
01:14:15,272 --> 01:14:17,452
I'll leave it to you.

832
01:14:18,325 --> 01:14:20,232
I'll go home by your car.

833
01:14:30,340 --> 01:14:31,093
Are you Osaki?

834
01:14:31,612 --> 01:14:32,746
I think you have been contacted by the police.

835
01:14:33,272 --> 01:14:38,592
It will take you there in 1hour.
