836
01:14:44,046 --> 01:14:45,606
Connect the line.

837
01:14:46,586 --> 01:14:49,706
The dynamite will explode in half an hour.

838
01:14:51,526 --> 01:14:52,346
See you.

839
01:14:53,825 --> 01:14:57,778
Anyone who has a grudge against the chairman will dynamite himself along with the house.

840
01:14:58,370 --> 01:15:00,116
I will make the announcement.

841
01:15:04,832 --> 01:15:05,986
I feel good.

842
01:15:06,399 --> 01:15:08,239
