843
01:15:08,472 --> 01:15:09,726
It's been 15 minutes.

844
01:15:19,653 --> 01:15:21,340
There's a lighter in my pocket.

845
01:15:23,509 --> 01:15:24,556
Look at me.

846
01:15:31,846 --> 01:15:33,739
OK let's go.

847
01:15:38,239 --> 01:15:39,539
