01:16:02,489 --> 01:16:03,822
Fire my lope.

851
01:16:06,236 --> 01:16:06,922
Hurry up.

852
01:16:07,776 --> 01:16:08,709
Hurry up.

853
01:16:12,012 --> 01:16:12,586
Hot!

854
01:16:13,359 --> 01:16:13,799
Hurry up.

855
01:16:14,446 --> 01:16:15,152
