868
01:17:22,864 --> 01:17:23,724
Forty minutes now.

869
01:17:24,204 --> 01:17:24,831
That's strange.

870
01:17:25,037 --> 01:17:26,464
Damn it.
They escaped?

871
01:17:27,732 --> 01:17:31,012
We have next choice.
Give me dynamite.

872
01:17:36,060 --> 01:17:41,020
Connect this dynamite to the fuse.

873
01:17:44,033 --> 01:17:44,646
Are you alright?

874
01:17:44,739 --> 01:17:45,613
I'm alright.

875
01:17:46,046 --> 01:17:47,773
They could be waiting down there.

876
01:17:47,799 --> 01:17:50,179
In the case, I use this dynamite.

877
01:17:59,983 --> 01:18:00,670
It works.

878
01:18:03,156 --> 01:18:04,770
Damn it.
They did it.

879
01:18:05,071 --> 01:18:07,485
Ok let's do it.

880
01:18:28,863 --> 01:18:29,549
Fukazawa!

881
01:18:32,398 --> 01:18:35,811
Just above him soon.
We are gonna set the dynamite on fire.

882
01:18:43,053 --> 01:18:43,739
Shit!

