01:21:24,427 --> 01:21:25,443
Mr. Nambada, right?

907
01:21:25,982 --> 01:21:26,419
What?

908
01:21:28,083 --> 01:21:30,115
I have a warrant for your arrest, please come with us.

909
01:21:30,529 --> 01:21:31,411
What?

910
01:21:35,119 --> 01:21:40,431
If they die, we have nothing to fear.
It's all Fukazawa's fault.

911
01:21:41,353 --> 01:21:42,400
Let's go.

912
01:21:49,736 --> 01:21:50,674
