917
01:22:11,350 --> 01:22:14,647
Help us!

918
01:22:29,941 --> 01:22:31,644
they are waving the flag.

919
01:22:32,379 --> 01:22:36,371
The cable car is stopped, so it might be an SOS signal.

920
01:22:47,783 --> 01:22:48,987
Oh he's Osaki.

921
01:22:49,401 --> 01:22:50,471
It's me.

922
01:22:52,838 --> 01:22:54,518
Oh Negoro.
What's happened?

923
01:22:55,283 --> 01:22:56,752
