01:23:25,012 --> 01:23:27,191
Little right.

931
01:23:40,071 --> 01:23:41,118
Come on.

932
01:24:01,892 --> 01:24:02,704
You go first.

933
01:24:13,385 --> 01:24:15,596
Thanks, bros.

934
01:24:18,674 --> 01:24:19,338
Hurry up.

935
01:24:20,873 --> 01:24:21,599
Hurry up.

936
01:24:22,349 --> 01:24:22,888
Hurry up.

937
01:24:35,499 --> 01:24:36,296
Negoro!

938
01:24:57,736 --> 01:24:58,501
Hurry up.

939
01:25:00,299 --> 01:25:02,518
That cable car will explode.

940
01:25:31,342 --> 01:25:32,053
I took him.

941
01:25:32,373 --> 01:25:32,983
Thank you very much.

942
01:25:35,264 --> 01:25:36,233
Uncuff him.

943
01:25:37,522 --> 01:25:39,740
Can you leave from here?

944
01:25:49,913 --> 01:25:54,006
You need to talk with me again?
I've helped you enough.

945
01:25:55,046 --> 01:25:56,725
I have nothing more to say.

946
01:25:57,569 --> 01:25:59,319
I'll be the one to tell you what happened today.

947
01:26:00,514 --> 01:26:03,702
Nambada just confessed to the UBE and Oyama's murder.

948
01:26:04,835 --> 01:26:06,530
Your Note worked.

949
01:26:07,467 --> 01:26:09,186
